reviews: So far so good! Lint gets stuck between the screen protector and the case, which is already annoying me, but other than that it is grea!
Purchased to wear working outside, and has become my favorite toque. So warm, and big enough to wear with a pony if I needed. Will buy in more colors.
Ordered a Men's Small as a female, and found it to still be quite big, except tight on the waist/hips. I am 5'8", and 125lbs.
Purchased as bedroom clock/alarm. Really like the auto-dim feature and the slow wake alarm.

review_title: Really great comfortable 1/4 Zip, but stitching is already starting to come undone
reviews: Really love this fleece top. The pocket on the chest is great for storing phone, but the stitching in the shoulders is already starting to come undone. Would probably order again.
Used for bedroom bookshelves. Stud expanders were not great, so used other items to hang the shelves.
Works well for what I was needing it for.
